      <title>碧桂园大亨分红 帝国陷入危机</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-30/country-garden-tycoon-collects-dividends-with-chinese-developer-in-crisis</link>
      <description><![CDATA[陷入困境的中国开发商碧桂园控股有限公司的亿万富翁董事长和与其家族有关的慈善机构从其房地产帝国中的一家服务公司获得了 5060 万美元的股息。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-30/country-garden-tycoon-collects-dividends-with-chinese-developer-in-crisis</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 30 Aug 2024 10:28:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>印度将与阿联酋讨论贵金属进口激增问题</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-30/india-to-discuss-surging-precious-metals-imports-with-uae</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度从中东国家阿联酋进口的贵金属激增，引发人们担心一些贸易商利用税收漏洞，因此印度正寻求与阿联酋重新谈判贸易协议。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-30/india-to-discuss-surging-precious-metals-imports-with-uae</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 30 Aug 2024 10:27:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>菲律宾对失踪市长提起洗钱诉讼</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-30/philippines-files-money-laundering-cases-against-missing-mayor</link>
      <description><![CDATA[菲律宾周五对一名前市长提起了洗钱指控，据信该市长已逃离菲律宾，目前因涉嫌与以中国为中心的在线赌场有关的罪行而被通缉。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-30/philippines-files-money-laundering-cases-against-missing-mayor</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 30 Aug 2024 09:53:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国人民银行在市场恐慌警告后重启债券交易</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-30/china-s-pboc-sells-long-term-bonds-buys-short-end-debt</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在数月外界猜测中国央行将进入市场之后，该国央行终于开始交易国债，以抵御强劲的债券市场上涨势头，避免基准收益率跌至历史低位。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-30/china-s-pboc-sells-long-term-bonds-buys-short-end-debt</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 30 Aug 2024 09:18:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧元区通胀率跌至三年低点，支持降息</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-30/euro-zone-inflation-slumps-to-3-year-low-boosting-rate-cut-case</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧元区通胀率跌至2021年年中以来的最低水平——这强化了欧洲央行在不到两周内再次降息的理由。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-30/euro-zone-inflation-slumps-to-3-year-low-boosting-rate-cut-case</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 30 Aug 2024 09:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国大型银行利润下滑 仍面临派息压力</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-30/china-s-icbc-plans-first-interim-dividend-as-profit-falls</link>
      <description><![CDATA[尽管利率下降导致盈利面临压力，但中国最大的几家银行仍听从了监管机构的呼吁，增加股息并支持市场。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-30/china-s-icbc-plans-first-interim-dividend-as-profit-falls</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 30 Aug 2024 08:48:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>非洲最大银行标准银行调整高管职位</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-30/top-africa-lender-standard-bank-shuffles-senior-executive-roles</link>
      <description><![CDATA[标准银行集团有限公司任命肯尼·菲赫拉 (Kenny Fihla) 为这家非洲资产规模最大的银行的副首席执行官，这使他成为集团首席执行官西姆·查巴拉拉 (Sim Tshabalala) 的可能继任者。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-30/top-africa-lender-standard-bank-shuffles-senior-executive-roles</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 30 Aug 2024 06:32:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
